  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Assistant Product Manager (Product Innovation & Development)",
  "description": "<p>We’re looking for an <strong>Assistant Product Manager</strong> who will play a key role in <strong>new product development (NPD)</strong> and <strong>portfolio growth</strong> for our regional markets. This is a hands-on role where you’ll work with cross-functional teams to turn ideas into products that reach millions of families worldwide.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Roles:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Drive <strong>new product development projects</strong> from concept to launch, ensuring consumer insights are translated into winning products.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with <strong>R&amp;D and packaging teams</strong> to shape product design, features, and functionality.</li>\n  <li>Manage the <strong>product lifecycle</strong> – from pipeline planning, SKU rationalization, to renewals and innovations.</li>\n  <li>Conduct market and competitor analysis to identify <strong>growth opportunities and whitespace</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Ensure products meet <strong>regulatory requirements</strong> across multiple regional markets.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with marketing teams to build strong product positioning and launch toolkits for local markets.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with sales, operations, and finance to deliver projects on time and within budget.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor’s degree in Business, Marketing, or related field.</li>\n  <li>3+ years’ experience in <strong>product management or new product development</strong>, ideally in FMCG, consumer healthcare, or personal care.</li>\n  <li>Strong analytical mindset with exposure to market research tools (e.g., Nielsen, Euromonitor).</li>\n  <li>Excellent project management skills — able to manage multiple launches across different markets.</li>\n  <li>A creative and proactive problem-solver with passion for <strong>product innovation</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>email - lucas.chang@swiftsearchglobal.com</p>\n<p>EA License No: 18C9495</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Lucas Chang<br>\nEA Personnel No: R1874043</p>",
